ISHGA
🚀 Advanced Topshiriq: Multi-User Blog + Interaction API
🎯 Maqsad:

Quyidagi barcha tushunchalarni real loyihadagidek ishlatish:

Murakkab model relationlar
Custom serializer logic
Advanced filter/search
JWT + role based permission
Admin customization
🧩 1. Model struktura (murakkabroq)

Quyidagi modellerni yarat:

👤 User (custom user bo‘lsa yaxshi)
username
email
role (ADMIN, AUTHOR, READER)
📝 Post
title
content
author (FK → User)
category (FK → Category)
tags (ManyToMany → Tag)
is_published
views_count
created_at
🗂 Category
name
🏷 Tag
name
❤️ Like
user
post

👉 Constraint qo‘shing:

1 user 1 postga faqat 1 marta like bosishi mumkin
🔄 2. Serializer (advanced logic)
PostSerializer:
author read-only
likes_count (annotate yoki method field)
is_liked (request.user ga qarab)
tags nested yoki slug orqali

👉 Bonus:

create/update da taglarni avtomatik create qilsin
🔐 3. JWT Auth

djangorestframework-simplejwt

Qo‘shimcha:

Custom token ichiga role qo‘shing
🔑 4. Permission (murakkab)

Custom permission yoz:

Rules:
ADMIN → hamma narsani qila oladi
AUTHOR → faqat o‘z postini edit/delete
READER → faqat o‘qiydi

👉 Custom class yoz (IsAuthorOrAdmin kabi)

